quest of his older son, Robbie.\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1007, \"end\": 1013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"score\": 0.9829766032946476, \"rank\": 0.017317238783520796, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 826}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"the same men's synchronised 10-metre platform event\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 917}, {\"ngram\": \"retirement\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"the request\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 988}, {\"ngram\": \"his older son\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His husband Lance Black, a U.S. screenwriter and director, and their two boys were among the crowd at the Aquatics Centre on Monday, cheering on Daley, 30, and teammate Noah Williams for each of their six dives.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1227, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1034, \"end\": 1039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\", \"score\": 0.9422214319938256, \"rank\": 0.06128226938001892, \"text\": \"Black\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\"}, {\"begin\": 1185, \"end\": 1198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His husband\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"a U.S. screenwriter\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1060}, {\"ngram\": \"director\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"their two boys\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1093}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"the Aquatics Centre\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1137}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1147}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"their six dives\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am so proud to have been able to decide to come back after two years of (retirement),\\\" a beaming Daley said after Monday's event, even keeping the door open to a further appearance at the next Games in four years time.\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two years\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1300}, {\"ngram\": \"retirement\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"a beaming Daley\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1334}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday's event\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1360}, {\"ngram\": \"the door\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"a further appearance\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1412}, {\"ngram\": \"the next Games\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1430}, {\"ngram\": \"four years time\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think most of that was being able to set an example to my kids that if you have a dream and you work really hard, it does not mean that you are always going to be able to achieve exactly what you want to but it's about enjoying the process and doing what you can to show up, to be the best person that you can be,\\\" Daley said.\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1781, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an example\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1506}, {\"ngram\": \"my kids\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1517}, {\"ngram\": \"a dream\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1542}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"the best person\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1751}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair fell short of upsetting China's Yang Hao and Lian Junjie, who finished nearly 30 points ahead after the six rounds to take gold.\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1816, \"end\": 1821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9930837683384397, \"rank\": 0.005100315665728048, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1824, \"end\": 1832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yang_Hao_(Sui_dynasty)\", \"score\": 0.5916864370256529, \"rank\": 0.40495867768596194, \"text\": \"Yang Hao\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yang_Hao_(Sui_dynasty)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yang_Hao_(Sui_dynasty)\"}, {\"begin\": 1837, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_Junjie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lian Junjie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_Junjie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_Junjie\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The pair\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1791}, {\"ngram\": \"the six rounds\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1906}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1919}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that did not take the shine off the experience.\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the shine\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1952}, {\"ngram\": \"the experience\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1971}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LOS ANGELES STILL POSSIBLE?\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me, this year ... is the happiest I have been in diving in all of these years because diving wasn't necessarily my top priority.\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2063}, {\"ngram\": \"these years\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2100}, {\"ngram\": \"my top priority\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, it was extremely important.\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2175, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But there is nothing more important than my children and being able to spend time with them,\\\" Daley said.\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2281, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2196}, {\"ngram\": \"my children\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2228}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2257}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I adjusted my training schedule to train once per day, Monday through Friday, and was then able to enjoy from basically train seven till 10 a.m. each morning, and then spend the rest of the day with my kids.\\\"\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2495, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my training schedule\", \"from\": 2298, \"to\": 2318}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 2337, \"to\": 2340}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2363}, {\"ngram\": \"10 a.m.\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2431}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2469}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2480}, {\"ngram\": \"my kids\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley's Olympic journey started in 2008 in the Beijing Games, when he achieved 7th place in the men's individual 10-metre platform event.\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley's Olympic journey\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2520}, {\"ngram\": \"the Beijing Games\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2557}, {\"ngram\": \"7th place\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2585}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's individual 10-metre platform event\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He carried on to win a bronze medal in the event four years later at the home Olympics in London after being one of the faces of the Games.\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2726, \"end\": 2732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999982737791, \"rank\": 7.787754385212937e-10, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 2657, \"to\": 2671}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2684}, {\"ngram\": \"the home Olympics\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2722}, {\"ngram\": \"the faces\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2761}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2774}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also won bronze in the synchronised 10-metre event in the Rio Games.\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2847, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2794}, {\"ngram\": \"the synchronised 10-metre event\", \"from\": 2798, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"the Rio Games\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2846}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His popularity only increased after he came out as gay in 2013.\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2912, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His popularity\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His personal life as well as hobby of knitting were featured in tabloids and his social media pages accumulated millions of followers.\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 3047, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His personal life\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 2930}, {\"ngram\": \"hobby\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2947}, {\"ngram\": \"knitting\", \"from\": 2951, \"to\": 2959}, {\"ngram\": \"tabloids\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 2985}, {\"ngram\": \"his social media pages\", \"from\": 2990, \"to\": 3012}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", 