 future plans\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The next Olympic Games will be held in Los Angeles in 2028.\", \"from\": 3336, \"to\": 3395, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3375, \"end\": 3386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999994302016, \"rank\": 5.228358056882827e-10, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The next Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3336, \"to\": 3358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Oh, gosh, I do not really know yet,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3443, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I went from being the youngest on the team in 2008 to now the oldest diver on the team.\", \"from\": 3444, \"to\": 3532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 3479, \"to\": 3487}, {\"ngram\": \"the oldest diver\", \"from\": 3503, \"to\": 3519}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 3523, \"to\": 3531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to kind of enjoy this moment and make decisions about the future of diving for me later on.\\\"\", \"from\": 3533, \"to\": 3632, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this moment\", \"from\": 3557, \"to\": 3568}, {\"ngram\": \"decisions\", \"from\": 3578, \"to\": 3587}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 3594, \"to\": 3604}, {\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They might be adding different events into the Olympic Games in LA ...\", \"from\": 3634, \"to\": 3705, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"different events\", \"from\": 3656, \"to\": 3672}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3695}, {\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3701}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I live in LA now.\", \"from\": 3706, \"to\": 3723, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 3716, \"to\": 3718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it could be, you know, a chance to do a second home Olympic Games,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3724, \"to\": 3803, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 3750, \"to\": 3758}, {\"ngram\": \"a second home Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 3792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But for right now, I just want to join this moment and we will see how it goes after that.\\\"\", \"from\": 3804, \"to\": 3896, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"REUTERS Olympics E-paper Newsletters Podcasts RSS Feed About Us Terms & Conditions Personal Data Protection Notice Need help?\", \"from\": 3897, \"to\": 4031, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3897, \"end\": 3904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"REUTERS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 3948, \"end\": 3956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RSS Feed\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Us Terms\", \"from\": 3958, \"to\": 3966}, {\"ngram\": \"Conditions\", \"from\": 3969, \"to\": 3979}, {\"ngram\": \"Personal Data Protection Notice\", \"from\": 3980, \"to\": 4011}, {\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 4017, \"to\": 4021}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reach us here.\", \"from\": 4032, \"to\": 4046, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4038, \"to\": 4040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertise with us\", \"from\": 4048, \"to\": 4065, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Advertise\", \"from\": 4048, \"to\": 4057}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4063, \"to\": 4065}]}]}"